3300 purchases made through the Department of Administrative and Financial Services, Bureau
3311 of General Services to allow school administrative units to participate in cooperative
3322 purchasing for the purpose of the purchase, repair or alteration of nonbuilding real property,
3333 including, but not limited to, an athletic field.
